---
title: HelloHero: Crumbed Chicken & Chips with Dill-Parsley Mayo & Cucumber Salad
description: It’s a classic, it’s a favourite for all, it’s the answer to your cravings, a steaming plate of chicken and chips. That’s right we’re trying our hand at this superstar dish, bringing it to your kitchen with a garlic and herb crumb for the chicken fillets, a must-have side of potato chips, fresh salad and of course a herby mayo. You won’t be needing that takeaway menu anymore.

